{"tid":990444,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣行人天橋網絡","createTime":"2019-01-21T14:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T15:53:35.000Z","uid":39608,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"406c22848f0cc17845d12ce5878c26cf866fd505","tid":990444,"uid":39608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:57:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A9%E6%A9%8B%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25A9%258B%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B5%25A1&d=rYg5mx6yknX5c4F1CB4In57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=f80784cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A9%E6%A9%8B%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1</a><br />\nWIKI有張天橋網絡圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8e/TWFootbridgenetwork2018.png/1500px-TWFootbridgenetwork2018.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F8%2F8e%2FTWFootbridgenetwork2018.png%2F1500px-TWFootbridgenetwork2018.png&h=9c8a6b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但準備要更新了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/50682915_1873485592778060_8735492386576138240_n.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=33c0b20f9d01aaa9887d531ea7749158&amp;oe=5CC1AEE5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F50682915_1873485592778060_8735492386576138240_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D33c0b20f9d01aaa9887d531ea7749158%26oe%3D5CC1AEE5&h=4c9bce18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/50608268_1873485649444721_1489042806218424320_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=42b10682377e8ed8335af0613ec74fb2&amp;oe=5CB8FB13\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F50608268_1873485649444721_1489042806218424320_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D42b10682377e8ed8335af0613ec74fb2%26oe%3D5CB8FB13&h=be451f8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/376443552482279/posts/1873489519444334/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F376443552482279%2Fposts%2F1873489519444334%2F&d=rYg5mx6yknX5c4F1CB4In57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ccb7d191\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/376443552482279/posts/1873489519444334/</a>"},{"pid":"52049f79b3b845f440e754a6018deca120052e7d","tid":990444,"uid":39608,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:58:22.000Z","msg":"之後再更新，由荃灣站行去荃灣西站，荃灣廣場 &rarr; 祈德尊新邨/灣景廣場 &rarr; 全城滙&rarr;荃灣西站<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）荃灣天橋陣即將完成最後一塊拼圖。新樓盤「全城滙」的五條行人天橋開通後，行人日後可由荃灣站直接經天橋步行至荃灣西站，不再需在如心廣場或祈德尊新邨返回地面再步行到荃灣西站，全程「堅離地」。<br />\n<br />\n由華懋和港鐵共同發展的荃灣西站新盤「全城滙」，預計將於2019年第一季入伙。根據公契，「全城滙」一樓設有五條行人天橋，分別連接如心廣場、祈德尊新邨及荃灣西站。五條行人天橋由發展商承擔建設費用，並須負責管理及保養。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4452/36878130984_27970b840c_h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4452%2F36878130984_27970b840c_h.jpg&h=1667c024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1052731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1052731&d=rYg5mx6yknX5c4F1CB4In57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=11e468c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1052731&h=6edec65e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1052731</a>"},{"pid":"3aaca1c88710d086bb02365930639d2938a9b34b","tid":990444,"uid":39608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:59:34.000Z","msg":"未來發展<br />\n<br />\n荃新天地2旁的億京項目發展後，將會興建行人天橋連接荃新天地2及橫跨關門口街、德士古道、楊屋道的行人天橋，屆時行人天橋網絡將連接爵悅庭、立坊及樂悠居。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣西站上蓋的海之戀商場落成後，預計亦會接駁至天橋網絡。"},{"pid":"93e66fb5edd5a12b3ec79ac7a5efc6ff38b08ccd","tid":990444,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:06:31.000Z","msg":"改名做堅離地城呀"},{"pid":"6de5c22fe2fefa567bdffae15999e36a6e46e0fb","tid":990444,"uid":91317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:09:28.000Z","msg":"德士古道駁埋熊貓酒店就一個 loop"},{"pid":"439c51854132845bd63887041064ef3f93bbaadd","tid":990444,"uid":200317,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"真心覺得呢種設計正啊 好過旺角係地面塞死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f248b205f4b471a657aa703098ea65da857aef","tid":990444,"uid":150400,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:15:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2db6473befd1dc888443dab3f66d734ed7ca3cc6","tid":990444,"uid":43518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"439c51854132845bd63887041064ef3f93bbaadd","tid":990444,"uid":200317,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"真心覺得呢種設計正啊 好過旺角係地面塞死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:17:11.000Z","msg":"地面太多人 元朗旺角等燈位過馬路勁多人塞住哂"},{"pid":"c4343d9916b84c613350507e5a1ff138a3268abb","tid":990444,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"最好畫埋愉景新城跨過青山公路到香車街嗰條.....但大涌道另一條有d難度, 兩邊無駁建築物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068a45f0017a415872e0200f71dda7c71fc50b1f","tid":990444,"uid":200317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2db6473befd1dc888443dab3f66d734ed7ca3cc6","tid":990444,"uid":43518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"439c51854132845bd63887041064ef3f